{"tid":1544884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試著不要說5 demands, 說free HK, democracy now","createTime":"2019-09-05T17:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T23:49:23.000Z","uid":54303,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc6ca7449117f67fda18596785acf2f0e126713","tid":1544884,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"後者外國人一聽就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且普選緊要過屠狗，有普選就屠硬，冇普選都會屠一批平息民怨。所以呢個時候應該大大聲同全香港、全世界講：「我要真普選」！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4da695de1507656c08811b2be908b82e63497c","tid":1544884,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4344f4d1cd5bb83c871758325520b649b9713e9b","tid":1544884,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae3dc7638af3a95ea9ac36df2c0aaa390e3d734a","tid":1544884,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:03:54.000Z","msg":"建議STAND WITH US果個唔使再講<br />\n唔夠具體 又唔知想鬼佬做D咩幫你<br />\n講TOPIC果個好好多"},{"pid":"c61b859689fedca282c572d2963765b332ae3d2b","tid":1544884,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e14ee2e926778bedefe453b7b44a613fdf4f00","tid":1544884,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae3dc7638af3a95ea9ac36df2c0aaa390e3d734a","tid":1544884,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:03:54.000Z","msg":"建議STAND WITH US果個唔使再講<br />\n唔夠具體 又唔知想鬼佬做D咩幫你<br />\n講TOPIC果個好好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"已經過左果個階段，而家係全世界都支持香港，但又唔太知點幫忙<br />\n所以要洗版叫佢地boycott china<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d25655764d1dd036bbf89902c2a24d5fc99571","tid":1544884,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7c9bb09f8a895cb25c3562cd72a97652730111","tid":1544884,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19e14ee2e926778bedefe453b7b44a613fdf4f00","tid":1544884,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae3dc7638af3a95ea9ac36df2c0aaa390